'''''Afagh''''' ({{lang-fa|آفاق}}) is an [[Iran]]ian [[newspaper]] in the [[Fars Province|Fars]] region. The [[concessionaire]] of this newspaper was ''Seyed Javad Bavanati'' and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1909.

